ZH: 班长负责带领同学们参加校园活动。
EN: The class monitor is responsible for leading classmates to participate in campus activities.

ZH: 班长要确保同学们按时到校。
EN: The class monitor must ensure that classmates arrive at school on time.

ZH: 班长需要管理班级的纪律。
EN: The class monitor needs to manage the discipline of the class.

ZH: 班长负责收集同学们的作业。
EN: The class monitor is responsible for collecting classmates' homework.

ZH: 班长应该带头示范，做好榜样。
EN: The class monitor should lead by example and set a good example.

ZH: 班长要保持班级的秩序。
EN: The class monitor must maintain order in the class.

ZH: 班长要与老师保持良好的沟通。
EN: The class monitor should have good communication with teachers.

ZH: 班长需要帮助同学们解决问题。
EN: The class monitor needs to help classmates solve problems.

ZH: 班长应该尊重每位同学。
EN: The class monitor should respect every classmate.

ZH: 班长需要协助老师组织班级活动。
EN: The class monitor needs to assist teachers in organizing class activities.

ZH: 班长应该代表班级发言。
EN: The class monitor should speak on behalf of the class.

ZH: 班长要做好对同学们的督促工作。
EN: The class monitor needs to supervise classmates well.

ZH: 班长需要鼓励同学们努力学习。
EN: The class monitor needs to encourage classmates to study hard.

ZH: 班长要关心同学们的生活。
EN: The class monitor should care about the lives of classmates.

ZH: 班长需要协调同学们的关系。
EN: The class monitor needs to coordinate the relationship among classmates.

ZH: 班长负责更新每周的课程表。
EN: The class monitor is responsible for updating the weekly schedule.

ZH: 班长要带领同学们参加校运动会。
EN: The class monitor should lead classmates to participate in the school sports meet.

ZH: 班长应该坚定地带领班级前进。
EN: The class monitor should lead the class forward with determination.

ZH: 班长需要帮助老师巡查班级卫生。
EN: The class monitor needs to help teachers inspect the cleanliness of the class.

ZH: 班长要与同学们共同努力，打造和谐班集体。
EN: The class monitor should work together with classmates to create a harmonious class collective.
